</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle (1)\quad \langle \phi (x),\psi (x)\rangle =\int _{a}^{b}\phi (x)\psi (x)dx=0,\quad {\rm {and}}}">
